{160}{Mast23}{He denies everything. And he says he knows who started
 this rumor . . .}
{161}{Mast24}{I think I know who the liar is. Liar!}
{162}{Mast25}{Reasonable. One moment. Are you sure? What about the other females?
 It cannot be. Be.}
{163}{}{抱歉，你们的种族注定灭亡。}
{164}{}{请原谅我得意忘形……我早就说过了！}
{165}{Mast26}{Without any proof, I'm afraid I can't believe you. Now, you will join
