{185}{}{你说服了我。我会加入统一体。}
{186}{}{我想要你的一部分……你的头！}
{187}{Mast35}{Of course! The mutants will survive! The mutants will rebuild this
 world! And only as a mutant, will you be allowed to live! Live. Die!}
{188}{}{活下去！}
{189}{}{去死吧！}
{190}{}{你只关心你的变种人和他们的统一体。}
{191}{Mast36}{I am no villain. You have no idea what I, or the Unity is about.}
{192}{}{那就告诉我你的目的是什么。}
{193}{}{你是个恶棍。你只是在否认自己的内心感受。}
{194}{Mast37}{I don't have to prove myself to you. Using your logic, that must,
 prove I am not a villain. It would be a hopeless cause to explain it to you. }
{195}{Mast38}{Oh? Please, what sort of plan might that be?}
{196}{}{我要在这个避难所引爆核装置。它很快就会爆炸，把你们全部送入地狱！}
{197}{}{我会杀了你，那样你就很难继续下去了，对吧？}
{198}{}{我已经说服了钢铁兄弟会，如果我被抓住并且没有被释放，他们会来这里进攻。 他们随时可能出现。}
{199}{Mast39}{You might be telling the truth. It doesn't matter, but I will let
 you go for now.}
{200}{Mast40}{You are lying. It will be the last lie that you tell. }
{201}{Mast41}{One moment while I check out your story. You might be telling the
